“托勒密的占星學之傑出印記”被描述為“能夠獲知他的時代之哲學與科學精神”。<ref name="tester60">[[#Reference-Tester-1987|Tester (1987)]]  [http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=L0HSvH96alIC&lpg=PP1&dq=Tester%20Astrology&pg=PA60#v=onepage&q&f=false p.60] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=L0HSvH96alIC&lpg=PP1&dq=Tester%20Astrology&pg=PA60#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20200201054204 }}.</ref>托勒密同時寫道當“物理學”被定義為[[哲學|哲學]]，並且他的恆星影響的敘述及說明是依據[[亞里士多德|亞里士多德]]提出的四種性質（熱、冷、濕，以及乾）觀點同[[宏觀和微觀|普遍統一性]]（或曰宇宙統一性）以及[[音樂宇宙|宇宙和諧]]的哲學概念做比較而表達出來的。<ref>[[#Reference-Tester-1987|Tester (1987)]]  [http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=L0HSvH96alIC&lpg=PP1&dq=Tester%20Astrology&pg=PA59#v=onepage&q&f=false p.59] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=L0HSvH96alIC&lpg=PP1&dq=Tester%20Astrology&pg=PA59#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20200216122630 }}; [[#Reference-Lehoux|Lehoux (2006)]] pp.107-109.</ref>他的要旨是在這樣的條件下闡釋占星學的基本原理，所以這樣的工作也是受人瞩目到的是'''對於其缺乏了直接的天文基礎在占星實證上而言它是不予考慮得'''：<ref>[[#Reference-Tester-1987|Tester (1987)]]  [http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=L0HSvH96alIC&lpg=PP1&dq=Tester%20Astrology&pg=PA64#v=onepage&q&f=false p.64] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=L0HSvH96alIC&lpg=PP1&dq=Tester%20Astrology&pg=PA64#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20200308143611 }}.</ref>

